        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Devils are evil with a silver tongue, and one of your ancestors dallied in darkness or made an infernal pact.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell List</strong> divine</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Skills</strong> Deception, Religion</p>\n<p><strong>Granted Spells</strong> cantrip @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Ignition], 1st: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Charm], 2nd: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Floating Flame], 3rd: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Enthrall], 4th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Suggestion], 5th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Wave of Despair], 6th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Truesight], 7th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Divine Decree], 8th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Divine Inspiration], 9th: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Falling Stars]</p>\n<p><strong>Bloodline Spells</strong> initial: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Diabolic Edict], advanced: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Embrace the Pit], greater: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Hellfire Plume]</p>\n<p><strong>Blood Magicâ€”Tongue of Flame</strong> Your tongue becomes laced with the fires of Hell, and you can either lash out at a foe with it or swallow it to make your lies more palatable. Either a target takes 1 fire damage per spell rank (if the spell already deals initial fire damage, combine this with the spell's initial damage before determining weaknesses and resistances), or you gain a +2 status bonus to Deception checks for 1 round.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feat-effects.Item.Effect: Diabolic Blood Magic (Self)]</p>"
